			<description><![CDATA[Raju swakar and Shalini:  Meditation takes regular practice as with anything you want to master.  The essense of meditation is to connect with yourself, the spirit, the soul which is light,  The practice is natural, as this is who you really are.  Meditation is a combination of thoughts and feelings, both together bring an experiene.  To experience your true self you need to disconnect from all outside influences (relationships, situations, matter).  as you begin to focus naturally you will lose the awareness of your body.  In this experience of light connect to the source of power - the Supreme Soul who is also light.  This connection brings love, purity and spiritual power (shakti) which you can then use in your life.]]></description>
